07:12.040 --> 07:12.640
Kalian semua,

07:12.640 --> 07:14.170
belajarlah daripada Toby.

07:23.260 --> 07:24.520
Guna lakaran Lucy ini.

07:25.020 --> 07:26.060
Perkemaskan garisan,

07:26.060 --> 07:27.460
terus hasilkan pakaian.

07:31.980 --> 07:33.180
Mesyuarat bersurai.

07:45.360 --> 07:46.060
Cikgu Yue.

07:46.800 --> 07:47.680
Saya nak tanya,

07:48.340 --> 07:48.880
